usdPppoeProfileAgent.name: usdPppoeProfileAgent

revisions.description: Added PADI flag and packet trace support.
The initial release of this management information module.

usdPppoeProfileAgent.contactinfo: Unisphere Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@UnisphereNetworks.com
usdPppoeProfileAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the PPPoE Profile component of the SNMP agent in the Unisphere Data Routing Switch family of products.

usdPppoeProfileAgentV1.name: usdPppoeProfileAgentV1
usdPppoeProfileAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the PPPoE Profile component of the Unisphere Routing
        Switch SNMP agent.  This version of the PPPoE Profile component was
        supported in the Unisphere RX 3.0 and 3.1 system releases.
usdPppoeProfileAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the PPPoE Profile application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when the duplicate MAC address indicator and AC-NAME were added.

usdPppoeProfileAgentV2.name: usdPppoeProfileAgentV2
usdPppoeProfileAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the PPPoE Profile component of the Unisphere Routing
        Switch SNMP agent.  This version of the PPPoE Profile component was
        supported in the Unisphere RX 3.2 and subsequent 3.x system releases.
usdPppoeProfileAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the PPPoE Profile application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when support was added for PADI flag and packet trace.

usdPppoeProfileAgentV3.name: usdPppoeProfileAgentV3
usdPppoeProfileAgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the PPPoE Profile component of the Unisphere Routing
        Switch SNMP agent.  This version of the PPPoE Profile component is
        supported in the Unisphere RX 4.0 and subsequent system releases.
usdPppoeProfileAgentV3.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the PPPoE Profile application in the Unisphere Routing Switch.
